snippet.title: Tales of the Heroes: Twin Brave (PSP) - Jude Story 「1st Mission」
snippet.description:
Name: Tales of the Heroes: Twin Brave
Platform: PSP
Release Date: Feb 23, 2012
Genre: Action game

Normal difficulty. First time doing this mission got me to level 9. Second time got me to level 20, the level of this recording.
